cdata.name: Spend
cdata.desc: The MoxyOne project aims to create a seamless and secure debit card and payment infrastructure for every company, project and ICO that issues cryptocurrency tokens. MoxyOne provides a debit card, wallet system and virtual debit card, allowing users to make purchases within company ecosystems and “real-world” merchants worldwide. Spend is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum blockchain. It is the fuel for the MoxyOne system.
